# sloop — auto-drive the default rig: accelerate through the city grid, carve a few
# turns, then handbrake-drift the bend and straighten out. 60fps.
# Controls: gas=UP, steer=LEFT/RIGHT, handbrake=SPACE.
# frames 490
down 15 UP
down 75 RIGHT
up 130 RIGHT
down 175 LEFT
up 240 LEFT
down 280 RIGHT
up 325 RIGHT
# a handbrake drift through the next bend
down 350 SPACE
down 356 LEFT
up 400 SPACE
up 415 LEFT
down 430 RIGHT
up 470 RIGHT
